title: Drew Brees, Eagles, Cowboys, and the Herd Hierarchy
itunes:title: Drew Brees, Eagles, Cowboys, and the Herd Hierarchy
description:
Colin discusses the inspiring story of New Orleans Saints QB Drew Brees, why the Philadelphia Eagles are facing more struggles, what the Dallas Cowboys do well and where they need to improve, and the Herd Hierarchy. Guests include Doug Gottlieb, Drew Brees, David Njoku, and Gary Myers.
